@node NEW_STUFF "What's new in this version ??"
@{" " link INHOUD}
                         @{b}What's new in this version ??@{ub}
                         -----------------------------

  - Click @{"HERE" link RULING_CHANGES} to see what has @{b}changed@{ub} in the General Rulings.

  - Click @{"HERE" link RULING_NEW} to see what is @{b}new@{ub} in the General Rulings.

  - Click @{"HERE" link CARD_CHANGES} to see what has @{b}changed@{ub} in the Card Rulings.

  - Click @{"HERE" link CARD_NEW} to see what is @{b}new@{ub} in the Card Rulings.
  
  - Combo list is improved.

  - Added Flavor Texts for Visions, Mirage, Tempest, Weatherlight and a part
    of the 5th edition.

  - Updated the Artists list.

  - Lots of other things you won't notice :))

@endnode
@node TODO "When will it be finished...."
@{" " link INHOUD}
                            @{b}What to do next....@{ub}
                            -------------------

  - Add the Fifth Edition Texts for all cards EXCEPT Artifacts, Black,
    Blue, Green and Red cards. These have been done.

  - Add current print-run numbers per card (Current lists have them
    already included, except for Alliances, Mirage, Visions, Fifth
    Edition, Weatherlight, Tempest and Portal as there is no information
    available from WoTC yet). Please note, that We removed this information
    from the current lists and made it available per edition in the
    @{"Printing Information" link MTG_CARD_RULINGS.guide/PRINT_INFO}.

  - Add flavor text for each card (Fifth Edition have to be done entirely)
   
  - Make an alphabetical list of all artists, including links to the
    cards they have made.

  - Add most wanted cards list.

  - ???


@endnode
