                             @{b}Joseph W. DeVincentis@{ub}
                             ---------------------

  Joseph W. DeVincentis is the editor of the  socalled "Devjoes List".  This list
  contains all descriptions of every card ever printed in Magic.

  He  can  be  contacted by Email at devjoe@wilma.che.utexas.edu or you can visit
  his  FTP site at ftp://wilma.che.utexas.edu/magic for the latest edition of the
  "Devjoes List".
  You can also visit his homepage at "http://wilma.che.utexas.edu/~devjoe"

@endnode
